data.description: Nestled on a corner lot in the town of Basin, this 4-bedroom, 1.5-bath home offers both space and convenience. Boasting not one, but two detached garages. Park your vehicles, store your outdoor gear, or create a workshop in the two detached garages. Property offers versatility and ample space for all your needs. schedule a showing today and discover all that this wonderful property has to offer!
